{"lemma":"رُبّاحٌ","slug":"رُبّاحٌ","root":"ر.ب.ح","root_slug":"ر-ب-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ب-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14447","n14448","n14451"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of رِبْح (ribḥ)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of رُبْح (rubḥ)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14447","headword_ar":"رَبَاحٌ","root":"rbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riboHN","text_ar":"رِبْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in two places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain small animal, resembling the cat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(So in many copies of the S.) F observes that J says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~abaAHu","text_ar":"الرَّبَاحُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwayob~apN yujolabu minohaA AlkaAfuwru","text_ar":"دُوَيْبَّةٌ يُجْلَبُ مِنْهَا الكَافُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been substituted as an amendment for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwyb~p","text_ar":"دويبّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in some of the copies [of the S]; but that each of these readings is erroneous: for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yjlb","text_ar":"يجلب"},{"kind":"text","text":"we find [in copies of the S] in the handwriting of Aboo-Zekereeyà and that of Aboo-Sahl"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuHolabu","text_ar":"يُحْلَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the substitution of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bld","text_ar":"بلد"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwybap","text_ar":"دويبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"was made by IKtt: in the copies of the S, moreover, we find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohaA","text_ar":"مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": and IB says that the passage in J's original copy, in his own handwriting, runs thus:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~abaAHu A^ayoDFA duwayob~apN","text_ar":"الرَّبَاحُ اَيْضًا دُوَيْبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAls~in~awri yujolabu minohu AlkaAfuwru","text_ar":"كَالسِّنَّورِ يُجْلَبُ مِنْهُ الكَافُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [But I find that, in five copies of the S, between"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alsn~wr","text_ar":"السنّور"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yjlb","text_ar":"يجلب"},{"kind":"text","text":", occur the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlr~abaAHu A^ayoDFA baladN","text_ar":"وَالرَّبَاحُ اَيْضًا بَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balodapN","text_ar":"بَلْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@somu baladK","text_ar":"ا@سْمُ بَلَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and I think it most probable that J intended to have introduced these or similar words, and therefore wrote"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohaA","text_ar":"مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbAH","text_ar":"رباح"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the appellation of a certain small animal, resembling the cat: and that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlrbAH","text_ar":"الرباح"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also the name of a country or town from which camphor is brought: this country or town is said in a marginal note in a copy of the S to be in India.]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14448","headword_ar":"رُبَاحٌ","root":"rbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~aAHN","text_ar":"رُبَّاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14451","headword_ar":"رُبَّاحٌ","root":"rbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(A' Obeyd, S, A, L, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaAHN","text_ar":"رُبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) the latter of the dial. of El-Yemen, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaHN","text_ar":"رُبَحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The male ape;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"simia caudata, clunibus nudis:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Forskål, \"Descr. Animalium\" &c., p. iii.:)] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one of an ape:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apes"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as a coll. gen. n.]: (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nSH","text_ar":"نصح"},{"kind":"text","text":", in explanation of the last, which is there said to be originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaAHN","text_ar":"رُبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaAbiyHu","text_ar":"رَبَابِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amolaHu mino rub~aAHK","text_ar":"اَمْلَحُ مِنْ رُبَّاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaAHK","text_ar":"رُبَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prettier"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than the ape."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~u rub~aAHK","text_ar":"رُبُّ رُبَّاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, A, K) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaAHK","text_ar":"رُبَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sort of dates"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of ElBasrah."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth.) ―         -b3-  Also, (K,) accord. to some, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~aAHN","text_ar":"رُبَّاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small young weaned camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small young camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaA$iyapN","text_ar":"حَاشِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender in the bones and meagre in the body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) but A Heyth asks, How can it mean small young weaned camels, seeing that a poet applies to it the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~","text_ar":"ثَنِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vnY~","text_ar":"ثنىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is five years old? and Khidásh Ibn-Zuheyr, in a verse cited by Sh, speaks of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rb~AH","text_ar":"ربّاح"},{"kind":"text","text":"breathing hard in labour, in order that her young one might come forth. (TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubaHN","text_ar":"رُبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["A","TA","L","Lth","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}